<div class="red">友情提醒：下方高难度，请非前端工程师或资深设计师绕道而行，慎防内伤。</div>
<br/>
<div class="form-horizontal">
    <div class="row-fluid">
        <div class="span24">
            <div class="control-group">
                <label class="control-label">模块背景色</label>
                <div class="controls control-row-auto">
                    <div class="colorSelect" data-value="{{modBGColor}}" data-tag="modBGColor"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="form-vertical">
    <div class="row-fluid">
        <div class="span24">
            <div class="control-group">
                <label class="control-label">自定义HTML</label>
                <div class="controls control-row-auto">
                    <textarea data-tag="html">{{html}}</textarea>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="control-group">
                <label class="control-label">自定义CSS</label>
                <div class="controls control-row-auto">
                    <textarea data-tag="css">{{css}}</textarea>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="control-group">
                <label class="control-label">自定义Javascript脚本</label>
                <div class="controls control-row-auto">
                    <textarea data-tag="js">{{js}}</textarea>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>